title: U.S. women who have given oral sex to a male in their lifetime , by age group
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Share of respondents for 10 number of Age groups.
The Share of respondents is appeared to be the highest at Age group 25-29 and lowest at Age group 14-15.
The difference of Share of respondents between the highest and lowest Age group is 76.0.
